      "text": "The Earth has three main layers. The\ninnermost layer is known as the\ncore, the layer in the middle is\nthe mantle, while the outermost\nlayer is the crust. The curst and\nthe upper portion of the mantle\ntogether from the lithosphere. The\nlithosphere consists of huge masses\nof land known as continents -\nAsia, Africa, North America, South\nAmerica, Europe, Australia and\nAntarctica."
